PrecisOrder which provides for: (a) the withdrawal from disposal of various mineral rights affecting numerous tracts of so-called "North Slave" lands in the Northwest Territories, in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims by the Dene Nation and the N.W.T. Metis Association; and (b) the revocation of Order in Council P.C.1989-624 in order to provide Echo Bay Mines Limited with a winter access road to their Lupin Mine works.

precis:
Order which provides for: (a) the withdrawal from disposal of various
mineral rights affecting numerous tracts of so-called "North Slave" lands
in the Northwest Territories, in order to facilitate the settlement of
land claims by the Dene Nation and the N.W.T. Metis Association; and (b)
the revocation of Order in Council P.C.1989-624 in order to provide Echo
Bay Mines Limited with a winter access road to their Lupin Mine works.
